<dl id="n42024e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42024e">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42024e"> 24(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> faith, repentance / &amp; love</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">That marvellous forgiveness is a free gift offered not for any outward act of the sinner; nothing is required from him but faith, repentance, and love. <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 117</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
